<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_05_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema624_05.css" />
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema626_02_0003.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_su_0003" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3, page_4">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="1_green" lang="y">
                새 크레파스 1개를 만드는 데 헌 크레파스 4 g이 필요하고, 새 크레파스 6개를 만드는 데 헌 크레파스 24 g이 필요합니다. 새 크레파스를 1개 만들 때와 6개 만들 때의 새 크레파스
                수와 헌 크레파스 양의 비를 이용하여 비례식을 세우고 살펴봅시다.
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">

            <div class="input_area">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <h3 lang="y">새 크레파스 수와 헌 크레파스 양의 비에서 이용한 비의 성질을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="img_row flex align_start">
                        <div class="picture_wrap">
                            <div class="img1"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_05_SU/624_05_0003.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="img2"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_05_SU/arrow_1.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="img3"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_05_SU/arrow_2.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt1">
                                <span>×6</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt2">
                                <span>1:4</span>
                                <span>6:24</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt3">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                                    <span>×</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                                <div class="example_box">
                                    <p>소수 한 자리 수이므로 비의 전항과 후항에 10을 곱해야 합니다.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article><!-- 1페이지 -->


                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">앞의 두 비를 이용하여 비례식을 세워 보세요.
                    </h3>
                    <div class="flex justify_center">
                        <div class="flex modification_wrap">
                            <div class="modification">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                                    <span>1:4=</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer3">
                                    <span>:</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="24" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modification">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                                    <span>1:4=1×</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer4">
                                    <span>:4×</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article><!-- 2페이지 -->

                <article class="page page_3">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        앞의 비례식에서 외항의 곱과 내항의 곱은 각각 얼마인가요?
                    </h3>
                    <div class="flex justify_center">
                        <div class="flex modification_wrap">
                            <div class="modification">
                                <span class="bg">외항의 곱</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                                    <span>1×</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                                    <span class="bg2">=1×4×6=</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="24" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modification">
                                <span class="bg">내항의 곱</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                                    <span>4×</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                                    <span class="bg2">=1×4×6=</span>
                                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6" text-align="center"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article> <!-- 3페이지 -->



                <article class="page page_4">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        외항의 곱과 내항의 곱을 비교해 보고 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.
                    </h3>
                    <div class="flex justify_center">
                        <div class="drop_down">
                            <span>비례식에서의 외항의 곱과 내항의 곱은&nbsp;</span>
                            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                                <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="">
                                    <option></option><!--최초선택데이터 생성 방지용-->
                                    <option value="같습니다."></option>
                                    <option value="다릅니다."></option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article> <!-- 4페이지 -->
                <article class="page page_5">
                    <div class="summarize_wrap">
                        <div class="summarize">
                            <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
                            <div>
                                <span lang="y">비례식에서</span>
                                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="외항의 곱" lang="y">외항의 곱</button>
                                <span lang="y">과</span>
                                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="내항의 곱" lang="y">내항의 곱</button>
                                <span lang="y">은 <span class=red>같습니다.</span></span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <span lang="y">1:4=1×<span class="star">★</span>:4×<span class="star m_bg1">★</span>의
                                    외항의
                                    곱은
                                    1x4×<span class="star">★</span>이고,</span>
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <span lang="y">내항의 곱은 4×1×<span class="star m_bg2">★</span>이므로 두 곱은 같습니다.</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sub_img_wrap">
                                <div class="sub_img">
                                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_05_SU/624_05_0004.png" alt="">
                                    <div class="arrow_img">
                                        <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA624_05_SU/arrow_3.png" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt_1">
                                        <span>1×24=</span>
                                        <span>24</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt_2">
                                        <span>1:4</span>
                                        <span>=</span>
                                        <span>6:24</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="txt_3">
                                        <span>4x6=</span>
                                        <span>24</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article><!-- 5페이지 -->
            </div>
            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType">입력토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">확인</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>